(44, 'Capacitance - Allen Physics', 'Kota  Rajasthan', 'Introductory Physics III', 'Slides', 'MAGNETISM,MAGNETIC FIELD,Applications of Geo-magnetism,Magnetic field of long Bar magnet,Magnetic shielding,Dipole - Dipole Interactions,MAGNETIC MATERIALS', 'Okeke Johnpaul', 'img44.png', '', '', '2011', '18', 1, 0),
